@startuml ch5_fig_state_pipeline
!include _style.iuml
title State diagram --- pipeline lifecycle

[*] --> draft : create
draft : nodes editable
draft : Run button enabled\nwhen valid graph
draft --> draft : Save / drag / edit
draft --> running : Run

running : worker dequeued
running : SocketIO room joined
running : live metrics streaming

running --> done : worker success\n(emit training_complete)
running --> error : exception or VRAM refusal

done : artefact persisted
done : results page accessible
done --> draft : Edit
done --> [*] : Archive

error : detail stored in task_results
error --> running : Retry
error --> draft : Edit + Retry
@enduml
